rectly to children; instead their blessing was invoked by prefixing the name with <i>mael</i> ‘devotee of’ or <i>gille</i> ‘servant of’. Since the 1930s the given name has been used widely in the English-speaking world, not just by those with Scottish connections."],"variants":[]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Attainment’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Malcolm de Luss - Fifth Lord of Luss was born in 1262, in Luss, Dunbartonshire, Scotland, United Kingdom as the son of John Luss of Luss. He had at least 1 son. He died in 1345, in his hometown, at the age of 83."},"et":{"1262–1345":"1262–1345","1290–1385":"1290–1385","1250–1315":"1250–1315","1315":"1315","from 1292 to 1333":"1292 kuni 1333","1345":"1345","1385":"1385","1262":"1262","1250":"1250","1290":"1290","Luss, Dunbartonshire, Scotland":"Luss, Dunbartonshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1262–1345":"1262–1345","1290–1385":"1290–1385","1250–1315":"1250–1315","1315":"1315","from 1292 to 1333":"vuodesta 1292 vuoteen 1333","1345":"1345","1385":"1385","1262":"1262","1250":"1250","1290":"1290","Luss, Dunbartonshire, Scotland":"Luss, Dunbartonshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1262–1345":"1262–1345","1290–1385":"1290–1385","1250–1315":"1250–1315","1315":"1315","from 1292 to 1333":"du 1292 au 1333","1345":"1345","1385":"1385","1262":"1262","1250":"1250","1290":"1290","Luss, Dunbartonshire, Scotland":"Luss, Dunbartonshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Malcolm de Luss - Fifth Lord of Luss est né en 1262, à Luss, Dunbartonshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni, fils de John Luss of Luss. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1345, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 83 ans."},"de":{"1262–1345":"1262–1345","1290–1385":"1290–1385","1250–1315":"1250–1315","1315":"1315","from 1292 to 1333":"von 1292 bis 1333","1345":"1345","1385":"1385","1262":"1262","1250":"1250","1290":"1290","Luss, Dunbartonshire, Sc